{{!
    @template core/html_table_cell

    Moodle html_table_cell template.

    The purpose of this template is to render a html_table_cell.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * text          Cell content.
    * type          (optional) td or th.
    * classes       (optional) CSS classes as a space-separated list.
    * attributes    (optional) Array of name / value pairs. The value can be omitted for shorthand attributes.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "text": "I'm a table cell!",
        "type": "th",
        "attributes": [
            { "name": "class", "value": "mytablecell" }
        ]
    }

}}
